text: Too many buses to cause jam but also helps me to get to the airport on my travels. Efficient arrivals

There's an overhead ramp bridge across the TPE that allows access to bus services going the opposite direction
Bit of a walk though

Especially enjoy bus 965 from Woodlands interchange to Punggol. Comfortably steady yet speedy bus rises along the well maintained TPE with scenic views of Seletar full of greenery. Conveniently located next to the famous coffeehouse That Coffee Place for great value for money and tasty coffee tea pastries and food. Friendly cosy comfy welcoming ambience for romantic intimates groups students tourists Expats locals and families.

Punngol on oneside and Sengkang on the other side.Heavy traffic flow during morning and evening peak hours on week days.Other times smooth flowing.
